WHAT THIS SYSTEM DOES
═══════════════════════════════════════════

TWO FUNCTIONS:
1. TRACKING: Manager pastes orders → system sends WhatsApp tracking auto.
   Webhook receives delivery updates from Meta. Dashboard shows status.
   (Still on Google Sheets — migrating to Supabase in Phase 1)

2. CAMPAIGNS: Upload CSV → save as contact book → pick template →
   map variables → send bulk WhatsApp messages to students.
   (LIVE on Supabase ✅)

